&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;This position will help develop and drive day-to-day user acquisition and retargeting campaigns via multiple channels. These channels include, but are not limited to, Google Ads (App Campaigns/UAC), Meta/Instagram, 3&lt;sup&gt;rd&lt;/sup&gt; party Ad Networks, CTV (Connected TV), digital sponsorships, licensor collaborations, and select others to acquire high-quality users who are likely to engage and monetize within Topps Digital’s suite of digital collectible apps (8 total apps - https://play.toppsapps.com). &amp;nbsp;This is an individual contributor role with significant ownership over acquisition strategy, campaign execution, optimization, partner management, and creative testing across multiple mobile apps.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
