&lt;p&gt;Fanatics Collectibles is seeking an Associate Account Manager to support and grow our NA Retail business across a portfolio of emerging and non-traditional retail accounts. This role reports to a Director of Retail or NA Retail Account Manager and is designed for an early-career sales professional looking to develop foundational skills in account management, analytics, retail operations, and channel development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is divided into two key areas of focus: (1) Retail Account Setup, Listings and Analytics (approximately 40% of the role), which involves building and maintaining the operational foundation that enables our retail partners to sell effectively; and (2) Account management and development (approximately 60% of the role), which covers professional team accounts, emerging sports-adjacent accounts, and energy channel doors — areas with strong growth potential as Fanatics Collectibles expands its retail footprint to convert more fans to collectors.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate is highly organized, detail-oriented, and eager to learn the mechanics of B2B retail sales. A passion for sports, culture, and collectibles is a strong cultural fit. This is an in-office role based in New York City.&lt;/p&gt;
